              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17908795268647700240">Since author Gail Carriger talked about this book on episode 191 of the Reading Envy Podcast, I’ve seen several of you reading it. Me too! This is an epistolary novel between two friends in Regency England but a version that also contains magic. It is very enjoyable as they navigate tricky witches and social expectations. I would have loved this as a younger me in particular.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


