<span id="freeTextContainer1076334717855064943">What a delightful novel! I thoroughly enjoyed getting stuck in Cecy &amp; Kate&apos;s story, which was a combination of magic and whimsy and friendship and romance. It did take me a little time to properly warm up to the epistolary style (as I don&apos;t read stories like that often), but it was definitely a story I was fully invested in by the end.</span>
  <span id="freeText1076334717855064943" style="display:none">What a delightful novel! I thoroughly enjoyed getting stuck in Cecy &amp; Kate's story, which was a combination of magic and whimsy and friendship and romance. It did take me a little time to properly warm up to the epistolary style (as I don't read stories like that often), but it was definitely a story I was fully invested in by the end.</span>
