    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1667708225" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3622205984351012391">An absolute joy to read, and one of my favorite books ever. I love the humor, the dual romances, and the mix of Regency England and magic. I can’t count the number of times I’ve read this book, but it’s a lot! If you haven’t read it and you love Regency romances, I highly recommend it. (Heat rating is similar to Georgette Heyer, i.e. no steam.)</span>

          </span>
        </div>


